$.fn.rmodal=function(a){if(a==="show"){$(this).show("slide",{direction:"down"},1000).addClass("active")}else{if(a==="hide"){$(this).slideDown(function(){$(this).removeClass("active")})}else{console.error("This type is not defined for opening a modal.")}}};$('a[data-type="rmodal"]').on("click",function(c){c.preventDefault();var a=$(this).attr("id"),b=$("#"+a);if(b.is(":visible")){$("#"+a).slideDown(function(){$(this).removeClass("active")})}else{$("#"+a).slideUp().addClass("active")}});